subject: Golf
ADT Championship (Golf)
lead_paragraph: The final two players for the final round of the ADT Championship, Christina Kim and Mi Hyun Kim, had to survive a four-way playoff in which Sophie Gustafson and Nicole Castrale were eliminated.
